manifests.contents:
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "ssu_mgmt"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "ssu_mgmt"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"

[dependencies]
base64 = "0.22.1"
chrono = "0.4.24"
crossbeam = "0.8.2"
diesel_migrations = "^2.2"
flume = "0.11.0"
futures = "^0.3"
jwt-authorizer = "^0.14"
log = "^0.4"
mime_guess = "^2.0"
regex = "1.10.4"
rust-embed = "^8.4.0"
serde_json = "^1"
serde_yaml = "^0.9"
thiserror = "^1"
tokio-util = "^0.7"
tower-layer = "0.3.2"

[dependencies.anyhow]
version = "^1"
features = ["backtrace"]

[dependencies.axum]
version = "^0.7"
features = ["macros"]

[dependencies.axum-extra]
version = "^0.9"
features = ["cookie"]

[dependencies.config]
version = "^0.13"
features = ["yaml"]

[dependencies.dashmap]
version = "6.0.1"
features = ["serde"]

[dependencies.diesel]
version = "^2.2"
features = ["postgres", "chrono", "serde_json"]

[dependencies.rdkafka]
version = "0.36.2"
features = ["cmake-build", "ssl-vendored", "gssapi-vendored"]

[dependencies.reqwest]
version = "^0.12"
features = ["json"]

[dependencies.seqtf_bootstrap]
version = "0.1.7"
registry = "seqtf"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "^1.0"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "^1.28"
features = ["full"]

[build-dependencies.vergen]
version = "8.1.3"
features = ["build", "git", "gitcl"]
